<view class="app-page fa"><view class="fa-head app-card app-card--glass"><view class="flex-row items-start justify-between"><view class="flex-col"><text class="fa-title">随访关联</text><text class="fa-sub">将身体数据趋势与随访/康养任务关联分析；异常指标会触发重点提醒</text></view><view class="fa-chip">{{a}}</view></view><view class="fa-sum flex-row justify-between"><view class="fa-sum-item"><text class="fa-sum-k">本周任务</text><text class="fa-sum-v">{{b}}/{{c}}</text></view><view class="fa-sum-item"><text class="fa-sum-k">异常次数</text><text class="fa-sum-v">{{d}}</text></view><view class="fa-sum-item"><text class="fa-sum-k">下次随访</text><text class="fa-sum-v">{{e}}</text></view></view></view><view class="fa-section flex-row items-center justify-between"><text class="app-section-title">趋势概览</text><view class="fa-link flex-row items-center" bindtap="{{f}}"><text class="fa-link-text">刷新</text><text class="fa-arrow">›</text></view></view><view class="fa-trends"><view wx:for="{{g}}" wx:for-item="m" wx:key="g" class="fa-trend app-card"><view class="flex-row items-center justify-between"><text class="fa-trend-title">{{m.a}}</text><text class="{{m.c}}">{{m.b}}</text></view><view class="fa-trend-val flex-row items-baseline"><text class="fa-trend-num">{{m.d}}</text><text class="fa-trend-unit ml-8">{{m.e}}</text></view><text class="fa-trend-hint">{{m.f}}</text><view class="fa-spark"></view></view></view><view class="fa-section"><text class="app-section-title">关联提示</text></view><view class="fa-tips app-card"><view wx:for="{{h}}" wx:for-item="t" wx:key="b" class="fa-tip"><text class="fa-tip-dot"></text><text class="fa-tip-text">{{t.a}}</text></view><view class="btn-secondary fa-tip-btn" bindtap="{{i}}">进入康养任务</view></view><view class="fa-section flex-row items-center justify-between"><text class="app-section-title">最近随访</text><view class="fa-link flex-row items-center" bindtap="{{j}}"><text class="fa-link-text">查看记录</text><text class="fa-arrow">›</text></view></view><view class="fa-list app-card"><view wx:for="{{k}}" wx:for-item="r" wx:key="d" class="fa-row"><view class="flex-row items-center justify-between"><text class="fa-row-title">{{r.a}}</text><text class="fa-row-time">{{r.b}}</text></view><text class="fa-row-sub">{{r.c}}</text></view></view><view class="fa-footnote"><text class="fa-footnote-text">提示：趋势分析为辅助信息，最终建议以医生端审核结果为准。</text></view></view>